title: Nespresso by KitchenAid
description: Introducing Nespresso by KitchenAid®. Designed to delight coffee lovers, this espresso machine features six pre-programed cup sizes and a die-cast, premium metal design. Choose from a wide range of 22 grand crus and whip up hot or cold milk froth to make your ultimate beverage. It’s elegant, intuitive and convenient. It’s design meets taste. Coming in December.
